# Push sau khi sua code

Khi ban vua chinh sua file trong repo nay (PHP, config, hooks, v.v.) va nguoi dung khong noi ro la chi sua local:

1. `git status` — kiem tra thay doi.
2. `git add` cac file lien quan (khong add rac tam thoi).
3. `git commit -m "..."` voi message ro rang, tieng Anh hoac tieng Viet ngan gon.
4. `git push` (hoac push len nhanh/upstream dang lam viec). Neu co nhieu remote ma nguoi dung khong chi dinh, uu tien `git push origin` hoac upstream mac dinh.

Khong them huong dan workflow nay vao README hay tai lieu markdown chi de giai thich push — nguoi dung muon hanh dong that, khong phai van ban.

Neu push that bai (mang, quyen, can pull truoc), bao loi va de xuat buoc tiep theo.
